<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include("../layouts/head") %>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="m-5 mx-auto border-light" style="width: 40%;">
        <div class="container card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center"><img src="/images/logo1.png" width="190" height="140"
                        alt="logoWippo"></div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center pb-5">
                    <p class="h1 fs-3 card-title ">Cambiar Contraseña</p>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <p class=" text-center">Ingrese una nueva contraseña. Es necesario la confirmes 2 veces. <span class="mute-text">Nota: Recargar está pagina requerira que vuelvas a enviar el correo de recuperación</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <form action="/authentication/changePassword">
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-md-6 form-group">
                                <label for="pass">Contraseña*</label>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="" name="Contraseña" id="pass">
                                <span class="errorP" aria-live="polite"></span>
                            </div>
                            <!-- form-group end.// -->
                            <div class="col-md-6 form-group">
                                <label for="passr">Confirmar contraseña*</label>
                                <input required type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="" id="passr" name="passr">
                                <span class="errorPr" aria-live="polite"></span>
                            </div>
                            <!-- form-group end.// -->
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Cambiar Contraseña</button>
                        <script src="/javascripts/validation.js"></script>
                    </form>
                </div>


            </div>
            <!-- card-body.// -->
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <p class="mt-4 mb-3 text-muted">© Wippo 2021</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>